DESERVES TO BE HERE.

12:48.917 --> 12:51.875
WELL, I DON'T,
BUT I KINDA THINK
YOU DO.

12:51.875 --> 12:54.708
YOU THINK I DESERVE
TO BE HERE?

12:54.708 --> 12:57.875
