EVERY OTHER SATURDAY.

14:01.041 --> 14:02.000
Girl: IT'S JUST
SO PUNITIVE!

14:02.000 --> 14:03.542
Woman: THAT'S
WHAT DETENTION IS.

14:03.542 --> 14:05.834
OH, MY GOD.

14:05.834 --> 14:07.959
