LIKE ABBY MORGAN.

14:07.959 --> 14:09.500
WELL, WHO'S ABBY MORGAN?

14:09.500 --> 14:12.208
YOU'VE NEVER
MET ABBY MORGAN?

14:12.208 --> 14:13.291
THE GIRL IS FROM HELL...
LITERALLY.

14:13.291 --> 14:15.625
