A JUVENILE DELINQUENT.

14:17.667 --> 14:19.750
IT'S ABOUT
SCHOOL POLICY, ABBY.

14:19.750 --> 14:23.542
BUT I COULD BE OUTSIDE
DOING GOOD THINGS FOR
THE CAPESIDE COMMUNITY,

14:23.542 --> 14:26.083
LIKE HELPING INVALIDS
OR PICKING UP LITTER,

14:26.083 --> 14:28.583
INSTEAD OF WASTING
THE DAY HERE--

14:30.000 --> 14:31.542
