14:31.542 --> 14:33.000
IT'S HOWDY DOODY TIME.

14:33.000 --> 14:35.458
Woman: SIT DOWN,
ABBY, AND THINK
WHY YOU'RE HERE

14:35.458 --> 14:37.542
IN SATURDAY
DETENTION
IN THE FIRST PLACE.

14:37.542 --> 14:39.041
BUT I COULD BE
DOING THAT AT HOME.

14:39.041 --> 14:40.041
YOU COULD PUT ME
UNDER HOUSE ARREST.

14:40.041 --> 14:42.208
