IN MY HOUSE ALL DAY LONG

14:42.208 --> 14:46.125
AND THINK, THINK,
THINK ABOUT WHAT
A BAD PERSON I AM.

14:46.125 --> 14:47.375
ABBY, SHUT UP.

14:47.375 --> 14:51.834
HELLO, EVERYONE,
AND WELCOME TO
SATURDAY DETENTION.

14:51.834 --> 14:54.375
DETENTION IS NOT
ABOUT FUN AND GAMES.

14:54.375 --> 14:57.375
