ASKING YOURSELF
THE QUESTION,

15:04.417 --> 15:08.000
"WHAT HAVE I DONE
TO GET DETENTION
IN THE FIRST PLACE,

15:08.000 --> 15:11.500
AND WHAT CAN I DO
TO IMPROVE
MY BEHAVIOR?"

15:11.500 --> 15:12.708
SOMEBODY'S MISSING.

15:12.708 --> 15:14.542
IT'S ME.
I'M HERE.

15:14.542 --> 15:15.667
JOEY?

15:15.667 --> 15:16.917
HEY, EVERYBODY.

15:16.917 --> 15:18.959
WHAT IS THIS,
SOME SORT OF
SURPRISE PARTY?

15:18.959 --> 15:20.917
OH, YEAH. SURPRISE.
BREAK OUT THE PIÃ‘ATA.

