15:24.417 --> 15:28.583
I HAVE SOME
IMPORTANT WORK TO DO
IN THE AUDIO-VISUAL ROOM.

15:28.583 --> 15:31.875
IF FOR ANY REASON
I HAVE TO COME OUT HERE
AND DISCIPLINE YOU,

15:31.875 --> 15:34.792
