TO YOUR BEAK,

16:09.959 --> 16:12.625
GET INTO A CAR
ACCIDENT WHILE
PICKING YOUR NOSE?

16:12.625 --> 16:15.375
NO, ACTUALLY.
THIS CHUMP RIGHT
OVER HERE,

16:15.375 --> 16:17.250
HE THREW A BASKETBALL
AT MY FACE.

16:17.250 --> 16:18.792
