BE THANKING HIM.

16:18.792 --> 16:20.333
CAN'T LOOK ANY WORSE
THAN IT DID BEFORE.

16:21.291 --> 16:24.083
IS THAT WHY YOU'RE
IN HERE, DAWSON?

16:24.083 --> 16:25.792
ATTEMPTED
MANSLAUGHTER?

16:27.959 --> 16:30.583
HOW ABOUT YOU, PACEY?
GET IN TROUBLE

16:30.583 --> 16:33.417
FOR DAMAGING
SCHOOL EQUIPMENT
WITH YOUR FACE?

16:33.417 --> 16:34.166
HE'S NOT TELLING.

16:34.166 --> 16:36.959
OOH. MUST
BE EMBARRASSING.

16:36.959 --> 16:39.834
WHAT DID YOU DO,
PACEY? MAKE UP ANOTHER
COCKAMAMIE STORY

16:39.834 --> 16:41.708
ABOUT SLEEPING
WITH A TEACHER?

16:43.041 --> 16:46.166
NO. AND IT'S NONE
OF YOUR BUSINESS.

16:46.166 --> 16:48.458
OOH. SECRETS
DRIVE ME CRAZY.
COME ON, PACEY.

16:48.458 --> 16:52.834
IF YOU TELL US,
I'LL GIVE YOU
A PIECE OF GUM.

16:52.834 --> 16:54.333
OH, YOU'RE SO COOL.

16:54.333 --> 16:56.750
