GRANT BODEAN.

17:48.542 --> 17:49.458
YOU SLUGGED
GRANT BODEAN?

17:49.458 --> 17:52.750
NO. IS THAT WHY HE
LEFT SCHOOL EARLY?

17:52.750 --> 17:53.959
YEAH.

17:53.959 --> 17:56.500
OH, MY GOD.
THAT IS MORONIC,
EVEN FOR YOU.

17:56.500 --> 17:58.875
I MEAN, GRANT BODEAN
IS, LIKE, THE KING
OF THE SCHOOL

17:58.875 --> 18:00.542
AND A TOTAL FOX.

18:00.542 --> 18:03.834
WHY DID THEY PUT ME
IN HERE WITH ALL YOU
VIOLENT OFFENDERS?

18:03.834 --> 18:05.417
WHAT'D YOU DO, ABBY?
YEAH.

18:05.417 --> 18:07.166
DON'T GO THERE,
DAWSON.

18:07.166 --> 18:09.291
OH, COME ON, ABBY.
WE TOLD YOU.
YEAH.

18:09.291 --> 18:11.875
LOOK, I DON'T WANT
TO BLOW YOUR MINDS.

18:11.875 --> 18:13.250
ABBY, WE CAN
HANDLE THIS ONE,
ALL RIGHT?

18:13.250 --> 18:16.250
I DON'T THINK
YOU CAN, PINOCCHIO.

18:16.250 --> 18:19.458
OH, REALLY.
HIT ME WITH IT.

18:20.458 --> 18:21.708
OK.

18:21.708 --> 18:24.000
YOU EVER BEEN
TO THE BOYS'
LOCKER ROOM?

18:24.000 --> 18:25.625
YEAH.

18:25.625 --> 18:28.917
YOU EVER HEARD
OF A LITTLE DRUG
CALLED ECSTASY?

18:30.250 --> 18:32.375
YOU EVER HEARD
OF AN ORGY?

18:32.375 --> 18:34.333
[CHUCKLES]

18:34.333 --> 18:35.458
THAT'S ALL
I CAN TELL YOU.

18:35.458 --> 18:38.625
