THAT SOME PEOPLE
IN THIS SCHOOL

18:38.625 --> 18:41.500
AREN'T AFRAID
TO EXPERIENCE A LITTLE
EROTIC PLEASURE.

18:41.500 --> 18:43.875
BUT...I DON'T
KISS AND TELL.

18:43.875 --> 18:45.500
THAT'S ALL I CAN SAY.

18:45.500 --> 18:46.875
SORRY.

18:48.875 --> 18:49.708
UH-HUH.

18:49.708 --> 18:51.750
YEAH.

18:54.875 --> 18:56.750
THIS IS SO
BREAKFAST CLUB.

18:56.750 --> 18:57.959
BREAKFAST CLUB?

18:57.959 --> 18:59.291
THE JOHN HUGHES MOVIE

18:59.291 --> 19:01.208
WHERE THE 5 KIDS
ARE STUCK IN DETENTION
ALL DAY?

19:01.208 --> 19:02.875
YEAH. AT FIRST THEY
HATE EACH OTHER,

19:02.875 --> 19:04.667
THEN BECOME REALLY,
REALLY GOOD FRIENDS.

19:04.667 --> 19:06.375
OH, YEAH.
THAT MOVIE STUNK.

19:06.375 --> 19:08.125
