GOT SOME KIND OF WEIRD
THYROID CONDITION,

19:11.000 --> 19:12.166
MOLLY RINGWALD
LOST HER GAWKY
INGENUE APPEAL,

19:12.166 --> 19:14.959
AND THE REST
ARE LANGUISHING

19:14.959 --> 19:16.708
SOMEWHERE
IN TV OBSCURITY.

19:16.708 --> 19:19.041
NO WAY! EMILIO ESTEVEZ,
HE WAS IN THOSE
DUCK MOVIES, REMEMBER?

19:19.041 --> 19:21.792
