YEAH. ARE YOU REALLY
AN ALIEN, AND WHAT
PLANET ARE YOU FROM?

21:46.291 --> 21:48.917
NO. AND EARTH.
OK, MY TURN.
NOW, WAIT A MINUTE--

21:48.917 --> 21:51.041
NO. THAT WAS
YOUR QUESTION.
THAT WAS A JOKE.

21:51.041 --> 21:54.125
LOOK, THERE ARE RULES
TO THIS GAME, AND
YOUR TURN IS OVER.

21:54.125 --> 21:55.917
NOW IT'S MY TURN,
AND I WANT TO ASK...

21:55.917 --> 21:58.041
PACEY.

21:58.041 --> 21:59.417
TRUTH OR DARE, PACEY?

21:59.417 --> 22:00.458
[SIGHS]

22:00.458 --> 22:02.208
