22:07.208 --> 22:10.041
TRUTH OR DARE,
PACEY?

22:10.041 --> 22:11.458
[SIGHS]

22:11.458 --> 22:12.792
DARE, TRUTH,
I DON'T CARE.

22:12.792 --> 22:14.208
FINE. TRUTH. PACEY,

22:14.208 --> 22:16.917
WHY ARE YOU
IN DETENTION?

22:22.667 --> 22:23.708
WELL, IT'S, UH...

22:23.708 --> 22:26.166
IT'S JUST--
UH, YOU SEE--
[CHUCKLES]

22:26.166 --> 22:28.208
WELL, YOU--
I WANT A--
I WANT A DARE.

22:28.208 --> 22:29.875
OH, COME ON, PACEY,
JUST TELL US.

22:29.875 --> 22:31.625
HEY. I WANT
A DARE.

22:31.625 --> 22:33.166
YOU ARE SUCH A WUSS.

22:33.166 --> 22:35.000
