22:37.792 --> 22:38.875
TO KISS...

22:38.875 --> 22:41.041
ON THE LIPS...

22:41.041 --> 22:42.834
FOR 10 SECONDS...

22:42.834 --> 22:44.917
JEN!

22:44.917 --> 22:45.917
W-WHAT?

22:45.917 --> 22:46.500
UM...

22:46.500 --> 22:48.500
UH-HUH.
[SIGHS]

22:51.125 --> 22:53.166
WE'RE WAITING.

22:53.166 --> 22:54.667
[CHUCKLES]

22:54.667 --> 22:56.083
THIS IS STUPID.

22:56.083 --> 22:57.708
NOBODY WANTS
TO PLAY THIS
GAME, ABBY.

22:57.708 --> 22:59.291
I--I DO...AND, PACEY,
YOU SAID DARE.

22:59.291 --> 23:02.125
