AS SHE SAYS.

23:04.750 --> 23:06.875
FINE. FINE.
WHAT DO I CARE?

23:28.875 --> 23:30.542
HAHHH...

23:33.917 --> 23:35.333
[PACEY COUGHS]

23:35.333 --> 23:37.959
OK. JOEY...

23:37.959 --> 23:40.375
MISS YOU-BETTER-DO-
AS-SHE-SAYS,

23:40.375 --> 23:42.166
WHAT'LL IT BE,
TRUTH OR DARE?

23:42.166 --> 23:44.583
NO. YOU SAID YOU
WERE GONNA--
AH, TA TA HA!

23:44.583 --> 23:45.959
TRUTH OR DARE?

23:45.959 --> 23:46.959
[SIGHS]

23:46.959 --> 23:49.083
TRUTH.

23:49.083 --> 23:50.417
[CHUCKLES]

23:50.417 --> 23:53.333
OK. WHO DO YOU LIKE?

23:53.333 --> 23:54.917
WHO DO I LIKE?

23:54.917 --> 23:55.917
YEAH. SIMPLE
QUESTION.

23:55.917 --> 23:59.667
WHO ARE YOU
IN LOVE WITH?
THE TRUTH.

24:02.750 --> 24:04.291
